            <h3>Privacy Policy</h3>
            <p>
              At MUSA, we respect your privacy. 
              <br>We do not collect any personally identifiable data. Information provided through our contact form is used only to respond to your inquiries. When you enter your name to receive a certificate after completing the quiz game, it is only used to personalize the certificate. This information, along with any details from the contact form, is not stored, shared, or used for any other purpose.
              <br>Any data collected automatically (such as usage analytics) is used solely to improve accessibility, functionality, and the overall user experience.
            </p>
          </div>
