            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="info3">
            <h3>Accessibility Statement</h3>
            <p>
              MUSA is committed to digital accessibility for all users, especially Deaf individuals who communicate using Irish Sign Language (ISL).
              We provide interpretive ISL videos, support screen readers, and prioritize mobile-first, inclusive design practices.
              If you encounter any barriers while using the platform, please <a href="/about-us#contact-in-about-page">contact us</a>. We will do our best to address your concerns promptly.
            </p>
          </div>
